---
title: Traditional Chicken Schnitzel with Rainbow Cherry Tomato Salad & Lemon-Butter Sauce
description: There’s nothing quite like the golden crust of a good old-fashioned chicken schnitzel to cheer you up – that’s just simple science. And as for condiments? We think our lemon butter sauce for the adults might just make for an unbeatable combination.
